COMPONENT NAME: RKM JDE World
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION: - Reverse engineering Knowledge Module to retrieve the tables for JDE World through IBM DB2 iSeries JDBC Driver (jt400). - This RKM is suitable for JDE World installed on IBM DB2 AS400.
If this option is selected, data tables are reversed.
If this option is selected, interface tables (ztables) are reversed.

DE System Short Name as (set % for all JDE System) : 00 Foundation Environment 01 Adress Book 02 Electronic Mail 03 Accounts Receivable etc ... Or you can specify a list of modules like '01','02','03'
Language used to recover the object description and comments. List of language : E English F French S Spanish

) values ( '<%=odiRef.getModel("GLOBAL_ID")%>', :SMOD_CODE, :SMOD_NAME )
